message.content: The likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are "cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE". This is because the paper discusses a new baseline for the Natural Questions dataset using BERT, which is a popular language model used in natural language processing tasks such as text classification, information retrieval, and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) and "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval), followed by "cs.LG" (Machine Learning), "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence), and "cs.NE" (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
